data.description: Welcome to this lovely home. As you enter you will walk into the living room with hardwood flooring. There is a main floor bedroom, currently used as an office. This house boasts 3 bedrooms and 1.1 bathrooms. The bedrooms on the second level each has built in drawers which allows extra space. The house has been wonderfully maintained with some updates. There's a home warranty with American Home Shields for the appliances. A must see!!!
